high_descs: Move forward towards the stove then turn left on the counter
Pick up the tomato from the counter
Turn to your left head to the fridge
Open the fridge chill the tomato in take it out then close the fridge
Turn left move few steps then turn right to the microwave
Open the microwave put in the tomato
anns.task_desc: Put chilled tomato in the microwave

high_descs: Walk to the stove and then turn left and look at the tomato on the counter.
Pick up the tomato on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Chill the tomato in the fridge and then pick the tomato back up and close the fridge.
Turn left and walk to the microwave to the left of the fridge.
Place the tomato inside the microwave and shut the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled tomato inside the microwave.

high_descs: move to the counter across from the fridge
pick up a tomato from the counter
move to the fridge behind you
chill the tomato in the fridge for a moment
move to the microwave to the left of you
put the tomato in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato in a microwave.
